{"tid":1551442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非既，同我入黎！！（大埔憤怒）","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:00:12.000Z","uid":173835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"891a4364810772203fc8f13730315f37bbb189d8","tid":1551442,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"我係大埔人，尋晚嬲到癲。<br />\n明明好和平，又冇衝擊，狗散我地散，啲細路咩裝備都冇！<br />\n指揮官話走，之後幾分鐘拖馬回頭打市民，下下打頭，DLLM ！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：</span></ins><br />\n<strong>我希望和理非既朋友，唔好睇少自己！</strong><br />\n其實我地既力量可以好大！<br />\n除左本身堅守信念，參與遊行之外。<br />\n大家仲有野係可以大大幫到依場運動！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要係工作及遊行以外的時間，盡量係WhatsApp,Facebook,甚至電話搵身邊所有朋友交流。<br />\n令佢地中立既變到黃，唔行動既變到多啲行出黎！</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">那怕自己只改變到一個人</span></strong>，但我地二百萬人就變成四百萬人。 <br />\n團結就係力量，我地要人！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。警權過大，毀滅世界！<br />\n<br />\n以下幾個細cases可用，簡單易明，滅絕人性：<br />\n1. 大埔青年冇犯事被打爆頭-<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QyNY_WpzV1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQyNY_WpzV1k&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=b846ec41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QyNY_WpzV1k</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF1v76t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF1v76t.jpg&h=a4f10577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 青年問警察良心係邊，又打爆頭-<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D4qFJfnkoMY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD4qFJfnkoMY&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=b7ade8b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D4qFJfnkoMY</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ONfzMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ONfzMA.jpg&h=d6e5f4a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 被捕少女求援被刻意踩手-<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xI91nwxNurs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxI91nwxNurs&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=cf76363c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xI91nwxNurs</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qX2voEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqX2voEZ.jpg&h=efddc467&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fef7bab8082268d75d7b3ede1be844f0f16e885b","tid":1551442,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"Take action la <br />\n<br />\n「懷疑有組織發佈大量fake news想搞散場抗爭」<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n今日 下午 美國領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=8b684da2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"1011c9e13065c907f011b9af44f6045591e0d61e","tid":1551442,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"支持警察<br />\n吞精互插"},{"pid":"8e71d5c77001b8e1c334b62e5fe5032d887d9b18","tid":1551442,"uid":173835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj